data.description: Welcome to this beautifully rehabbed 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch home, ready for its new owner. With a modern and open floor plan, this home offers seamless flow and elegance. Every corner of this property has seen updates that blend style with functionality, from the landscaped exterior to the high-efficiency appliances within.    Highlights of the transformation include 2019: Enhanced landscaping and security with exterior cameras. 2020: Upgrades to the garage, bathrooms, laundry room, and kitchen, including new Samsung appliances and interior lighting improvements. 2021: New windows, doors, and kitchen renovations with Quartz countertops and vinyl flooring.2022: Water softener installation, bathroom revamps with modern fixtures, whole-house painting, and garage organization solutions. 2023: New vinyl flooring and white trim in all three bedrooms.  From the ground up, every update has been carefully chosen to ensure comfort, convenience, and beauty. This home is not just a living space but a testament to quality and attention to detail. Don't miss the chance to see this exceptional property for yourself. It's more than ready to welcome you home.
